{"image_id": "JNPR_2014_page_46", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [37.5, 35.2, 197.2, 62.8]}, {"text": "Gross Margins", "bbox": [37.5, 83.4, 175.7, 112.0]}, {"text": "The following table presents gross margins (in millions, except percentages):", "bbox": [37.5, 133.2, 690.2, 160.8]}, {"text": "2014 Compared to 2013", "bbox": [37.5, 470.4, 250.9, 498.1]}, {"text": "Product gross margin decreased as a percentage of product net revenues in 2014, compared to 2013, primarily due to an increase in cost of", "bbox": [37.5, 520.4, 1249.6, 548.1]}, {"text": "revenues. The increase in cost of revenues was primarily due to asset write-downs of $41.5 million for product rationalizations in connection", "bbox": [37.5, 545.4, 1254.7, 573.1]}, {"text": "with our 2014 Restructuring Plan and $20.7 million in connection with an industry-wide memory product quality defect in a component from a", "bbox": [37.5, 570.4, 1254.7, 598.1]}, {"text": "third-party supplier. Excluding the costs of the restructuring and component defect, product gross margin as a percentage of net revenues", "bbox": [37.5, 595.4, 1254.7, 623.1]}, {"text": "improved slightly primarily due to the favorability in product mix in the 2014 period.", "bbox": [37.5, 620.4, 758.4, 648.1]}, {"text": "Service gross margin as a percentage of service net revenues decreased slightly in 2014, compared to 2013, primarily due to an increase in labor", "bbox": [37.5, 670.4, 1254.7, 698.1]}, {"text": "and logistics delivery costs to support new contracts and product introductions.", "bbox": [37.5, 695.4, 706.9, 723.1]}, {"text": "2013 Compared to 2012", "bbox": [37.5, 745.4, 250.9, 773.1]}, {"text": "Product gross margin percentage increased slightly in 2013, compared to 2012, primarily due to higher restructuring and other charges recorded", "bbox": [37.5, 795.4, 1254.7, 823.1]}, {"text": "in 2012, partially offset by higher inventory provisions in 2013 for legacy platforms. Product gross margin benefited from cost reductions in the", "bbox": [37.5, 820.4, 1254.7, 848.1]}, {"text": "supply chain in 2013, which more than offset the impact of higher pricing discounts.", "bbox": [37.5, 845.4, 752.2, 873.1]}, {"text": "Service gross margin as a percentage of service net revenues increased in 2013, compared to 2012, primarily due to higher service revenues and", "bbox": [37.5, 895.4, 1254.7, 923.1]}, {"text": "greater efficiency in the delivery of services.", "bbox": [37.5, 920.4, 419.9, 948.1]}, {"text": "44", "bbox": [633.0, 993.4, 664.2, 1021.1]}, {"text": "Years Ended December 31,", "bbox": [722.7, 179.6, 924.4, 203.0]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [429.7, 209.6, 471.4, 233.0]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [560.7, 209.6, 602.4, 233.0]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [690.5, 209.6, 732.2, 233.0]}, {"text": "2014 vs. 2013", "bbox": [847.5, 209.6, 949.7, 233.0]}, {"text": "2013 vs. 2012", "bbox": [1089.0, 209.6, 1191.4, 233.0]}, {"text": "$ Change", "bbox": [802.0, 239.9, 877.4, 263.2]}, {"text": "% Change", "bbox": [901.7, 235.4, 1021.4, 263.2]}, {"text": "$ Change", "bbox": [1037.0, 239.9, 1112.4, 263.2]}, {"text": "% Change", "bbox": [1153.7, 239.9, 1237.4, 263.2]}, {"text": "Product gross margin", "bbox": [40.5, 265.4, 229.2, 293.1]}, {"text": "$ 2,121.9", "bbox": [389.2, 265.4, 486.7, 293.1]}, {"text": "$ 2,243.3", "bbox": [515.0, 265.4, 616.7, 293.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [645.0, 265.4, 661.6, 293.1]}, {"text": "2,058.1", "bbox": [678.7, 265.4, 746.4, 293.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [774.7, 265.4, 796.7, 293.1]}, {"text": "(121.4 )", "bbox": [829.5, 265.4, 906.9, 293.1]}, {"text": "(5)%", "bbox": [935.5, 265.4, 987.7, 293.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1016.2, 265.4, 1038.2, 293.1]}, {"text": "185.2", "bbox": [1065.7, 265.4, 1135.4, 293.1]}, {"text": "9%", "bbox": [1177.5, 265.4, 1215.7, 293.1]}, {"text": "Percentage of product revenues", "bbox": [40.5, 294.9, 316.4, 322.6]}, {"text": "62.2 %", "bbox": [440.5, 294.9, 520.2, 322.6]}, {"text": "63.7 %", "bbox": 